name: La Petite Provence
description: Digital modified version out of one of our original acrylic paintings. In general these paintings size from 80x100cm up to 100x200cm.This is a new experiment, offering limited edition NFTs like those LE physical prints we do, well below our market price, in Tezos, so the people willing to collect an original certified work from an artist, can make it. There will be no more editions like this, and no NFT will be made from this work. Can be considered your entry door to art market or an investment
